data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER - Introducing an exquisite historical home set on three expansive lots. Extensively updated, this remarkable residence features a freshly painted exterior (2023) and interior and a fully remodeled kitchen, complete with a chef's kitchen, new appliances, and a six-burner professional stove with a griddle. Outside, enjoy the allure of brick walkways, inviting entertainment spaces, a New Orleans style courtyard, a private wine cellar, and a mesmerizing fountain. Inside, experience spaciousness with high ceilings, hardwood floors, and timeless charm. This 4-bed/3-bath property boasts two living room spaces, a study and an upstairs retreat. Prepare to be enchanted by the perfect blend of history and modern luxury in this extraordinary home. BRAND NEW HVAC AND WATER HEATER!
